{
  "spec": {
    "title": "Container Timing API",
    "url": "https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/"
  },
  "algorithms": [
    {
      "name": "create a container timing record",
      "href": "https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#create-a-container-timing-record",
      "html": "To <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"create-a-container-timing-record\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">create a Container Timing Record</dfn> given a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/paint-timing/#painttimingmixin-paint-timing-info\" id=\"ref-for-painttimingmixin-paint-timing-info②\">paint timing info</a> <var>paintTimingInfo</var> and a <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#idl-DOMString\" id=\"ref-for-idl-DOMString⑥\">DOMString</a></code> <var>identifier</var>, perform the following steps:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>record</var> be a new <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#container-timing-record-container-timing-record\" id=\"ref-for-container-timing-record-container-timing-record①\">Container Timing Record</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Set <var>record</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#container-timing-record-painttiminginfo\" id=\"ref-for-container-timing-record-painttiminginfo\">paintTimingInfo</a> to <var>paintTimingInfo</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Set <var>record</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#container-timing-record-identifier\" id=\"ref-for-container-timing-record-identifier\">identifier</a> to <var>identifier</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Return <var>record</var>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "handle element painted for container timing",
      "html": "When an element is painted and the user agent needs to handle container timing updates, given a <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#document\" id=\"ref-for-document①\">Document</a></code> <var>document</var>, a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/paint-timing/#painttimingmixin-paint-timing-info\" id=\"ref-for-painttimingmixin-paint-timing-info③\">paint timing info</a> <var>paintTimingInfo</var>, an <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#element\" id=\"ref-for-element①④\">Element</a></code> <var>element</var>, and a <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/geometry-1/#domrectreadonly\" id=\"ref-for-domrectreadonly②\">DOMRectReadOnly</a></code> <var>intersectionRect</var>, perform the following steps:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>element</var> does not <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#contribute-to-container-timing\" id=\"ref-for-contribute-to-container-timing\">Contribute to container timing</a>, return.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>containerRoot</var> be the result of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#get-the-container-root-element\" id=\"ref-for-get-the-container-root-element\">get the container root element</a> given <var>element</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>containerRoot</var> is null, return.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>record</var> be the entry in <var>document</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#container-root-records-map\" id=\"ref-for-container-root-records-map①\">container root records map</a> for <var>containerRoot</var>. If no such entry exists, set <var>record</var> to the result of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#create-a-container-timing-record\" id=\"ref-for-create-a-container-timing-record\">create a Container Timing Record</a> given <var>paintTimingInfo</var> and the value of <var>containerRoot</var>’s [^containertiming^] content attribute; then add (<var>containerRoot</var> → <var>record</var>) to <var>document</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#container-root-records-map\" id=\"ref-for-container-root-records-map②\">container root records map</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>enclosingRect</var> be the smallest enclosing rectangle of <var>intersectionRect</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#maybe-update-the-last-new-painted-area\" id=\"ref-for-maybe-update-the-last-new-painted-area\">Maybe update the last new painted area</a> for <var>record</var> given <var>document</var>, <var>containerRoot</var>, <var>element</var>, <var>enclosingRect</var>, and <var>paintTimingInfo</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Mark the <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#document\" id=\"ref-for-document②\">Document</a></code> as having pending container timing changes.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "emit container timing entries",
      "html": "When asked to emit container timing entries for a <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#document\" id=\"ref-for-document③\">Document</a></code> <var>document</var>, perform the following steps. This should be called once per frame after all paint operations have been processed:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>document</var> does not have pending container timing changes, return.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#map-iterate\" id=\"ref-for-map-iterate\">For each</a> <var>containerRoot</var> → <var>record</var> of <var>document</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#container-root-records-map\" id=\"ref-for-container-root-records-map③\">container root records map</a>:",
          "rationale": "if",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>If <var>record</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#container-timing-record-haspendingchanges\" id=\"ref-for-container-timing-record-haspendingchanges\">hasPendingChanges</a> is false, continue.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#create-a-container-timing-entry\" id=\"ref-for-create-a-container-timing-entry\">Create a Container Timing entry</a> given <var>record</var> and <var>containerRoot</var>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Set <var>record</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#container-timing-record-haspendingchanges\" id=\"ref-for-container-timing-record-haspendingchanges①\">hasPendingChanges</a> to false.</p>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Mark the <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#document\" id=\"ref-for-document④\">Document</a></code> as no longer having pending container timing changes.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "get the parent container root element",
      "href": "https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#get-the-parent-container-root-element",
      "html": "To <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"get-the-parent-container-root-element\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">get the parent container root element</dfn> given an <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#element\" id=\"ref-for-element①⑤\">Element</a></code> <var>element</var>, perform the following steps:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>parent</var> be <var>element</var>’s parentElement.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>parent</var> is null, return null.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Return the result of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#get-the-container-root-element\" id=\"ref-for-get-the-container-root-element①\">get the container root element</a> given <var>parent</var>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "determine contribution to container timing",
      "html": "To determine whether an <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#element\" id=\"ref-for-element①⑦\">Element</a></code> <var>element</var> contributes to the container timing of a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#container-root\" id=\"ref-for-container-root①⓪\">container root</a> <var>containerRoot</var>:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>element</var> is null, return false.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>element</var> is in a shadow tree, return false.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>element</var> is not a descendant of <var>containerRoot</var>, return false.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>element</var> is within an <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#ignored-subtree\" id=\"ref-for-ignored-subtree③\">ignored subtree</a>, return false.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Return true.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "get the container root element",
      "href": "https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#get-the-container-root-element",
      "html": "To <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"get-the-container-root-element\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">get the container root element</dfn> given an <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#element\" id=\"ref-for-element①⑧\">Element</a></code> <var>element</var>, perform the following steps:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>element</var> is null, return null.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>element</var>’s [^containertiming^] content attribute is present, return <var>element</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>element</var>’s parentElement is not null, return the result of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#get-the-container-root-element\" id=\"ref-for-get-the-container-root-element②\">get the container root element</a> given <var>element</var>’s parentElement.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Return null.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "maybe update last new painted area",
      "href": "https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#maybe-update-the-last-new-painted-area",
      "html": "To <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"maybe-update-the-last-new-painted-area\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">maybe update the last new painted area</dfn> for a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#container-timing-record-container-timing-record\" id=\"ref-for-container-timing-record-container-timing-record②\">Container Timing Record</a> <var>record</var> given a <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#document\" id=\"ref-for-document⑤\">Document</a></code> <var>document</var>, a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#container-root\" id=\"ref-for-container-root①①\">container root</a> <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#element\" id=\"ref-for-element①⑨\">Element</a></code> <var>containerRoot</var>, an <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#element\" id=\"ref-for-element②⓪\">Element</a></code> <var>element</var>, a <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/geometry-1/#domrectreadonly\" id=\"ref-for-domrectreadonly③\">DOMRectReadOnly</a></code> <var>enclosingRect</var>, and a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/paint-timing/#painttimingmixin-paint-timing-info\" id=\"ref-for-painttimingmixin-paint-timing-info④\">paint timing info</a> <var>paintTimingInfo</var>, perform the following steps:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>paintedRegion</var> be <var>record</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#container-timing-record-paintedregion\" id=\"ref-for-container-timing-record-paintedregion\">paintedRegion</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>paintedRegion</var> fully contains <var>enclosingRect</var>, return.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Set <var>record</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#container-timing-record-paintedregion\" id=\"ref-for-container-timing-record-paintedregion①\">paintedRegion</a> to the union of <var>paintedRegion</var> and <var>enclosingRect</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Set <var>record</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#container-timing-record-lastnewpaintedareapainttiminginfo\" id=\"ref-for-container-timing-record-lastnewpaintedareapainttiminginfo\">lastNewPaintedAreaPaintTimingInfo</a> to <var>paintTimingInfo</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Set <var>record</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#container-timing-record-lastnewpaintedareaelement\" id=\"ref-for-container-timing-record-lastnewpaintedareaelement\">lastNewPaintedAreaElement</a> to <var>element</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Set <var>record</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#container-timing-record-haspendingchanges\" id=\"ref-for-container-timing-record-haspendingchanges②\">hasPendingChanges</a> to true.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>containerRoot</var>’s [^containertiming-ignore^] content attribute is present, return.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>parentContainerRoot</var> be the result of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#get-the-parent-container-root-element\" id=\"ref-for-get-the-parent-container-root-element\">get the parent container root element</a> given <var>containerRoot</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>parentContainerRoot</var> is null, return.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>parentRecord</var> be the entry in <var>document</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#container-root-records-map\" id=\"ref-for-container-root-records-map④\">container root records map</a> for <var>parentContainerRoot</var>. If no such entry exists, set <var>parentRecord</var> to the result of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#create-a-container-timing-record\" id=\"ref-for-create-a-container-timing-record①\">create a Container Timing Record</a> given <var>paintTimingInfo</var> and the value of <var>parentContainerRoot</var>’s [^containertiming^] content attribute; then add (<var>parentContainerRoot</var> → <var>parentRecord</var>) to <var>document</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#container-root-records-map\" id=\"ref-for-container-root-records-map⑤\">container root records map</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#maybe-update-the-last-new-painted-area\" id=\"ref-for-maybe-update-the-last-new-painted-area①\">Maybe update the last new painted area</a> for <var>parentRecord</var> given <var>document</var>, <var>parentContainerRoot</var>, <var>element</var>, <var>enclosingRect</var>, and <var>paintTimingInfo</var>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "create a container timing entry",
      "href": "https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#create-a-container-timing-entry",
      "html": "In order to <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"create-a-container-timing-entry\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">create a Container Timing entry</dfn> given a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#container-timing-record-container-timing-record\" id=\"ref-for-container-timing-record-container-timing-record③\">Container Timing Record</a> <var>record</var> and a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#container-root\" id=\"ref-for-container-root①②\">container root</a> <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#element\" id=\"ref-for-element②①\">Element</a></code> <var>containerRoot</var>, the user agent must perform the following steps:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>entry</var> be a new <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#performancecontainertiming\" id=\"ref-for-performancecontainertiming⑦\">PerformanceContainerTiming</a></code> entry with its:</p>\n      <ul>\n       <li data-md=\"\">\n        <p><code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/performance-timeline/#dom-performanceentry-entrytype\" id=\"ref-for-dom-performanceentry-entrytype①\">entryType</a></code> set to \"<code>container</code>\"</p>\n       </li><li data-md=\"\">\n        <p><code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/performance-timeline/#dom-performanceentry-name\" id=\"ref-for-dom-performanceentry-name①\">name</a></code> set to the empty string</p>\n       </li><li data-md=\"\">\n        <p><code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/performance-timeline/#dom-performanceentry-starttime\" id=\"ref-for-dom-performanceentry-starttime①\">startTime</a></code> set to <var>record</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#container-timing-record-lastnewpaintedareapainttiminginfo\" id=\"ref-for-container-timing-record-lastnewpaintedareapainttiminginfo①\">lastNewPaintedAreaPaintTimingInfo</a>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/paint-timing/#dom-painttimingmixin-painttime\" id=\"ref-for-dom-painttimingmixin-painttime\">paintTime</a></code></p>\n       </li><li data-md=\"\">\n        <p><code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/performance-timeline/#dom-performanceentry-duration\" id=\"ref-for-dom-performanceentry-duration①\">duration</a></code> set to 0</p>\n       </li><li data-md=\"\">\n        <p><code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#dom-performancecontainertiming-identifier\" id=\"ref-for-dom-performancecontainertiming-identifier②\">identifier</a></code> set to <var>record</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#container-timing-record-identifier\" id=\"ref-for-container-timing-record-identifier①\">identifier</a></p>\n       </li><li data-md=\"\">\n        <p><code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#dom-performancecontainertiming-firstrendertime\" id=\"ref-for-dom-performancecontainertiming-firstrendertime①\">firstRenderTime</a></code> set to <var>record</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#container-timing-record-painttiminginfo\" id=\"ref-for-container-timing-record-painttiminginfo①\">paintTimingInfo</a>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/paint-timing/#dom-painttimingmixin-painttime\" id=\"ref-for-dom-painttimingmixin-painttime①\">paintTime</a></code></p>\n       </li><li data-md=\"\">\n        <p><code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#dom-performancecontainertiming-intersectionrect\" id=\"ref-for-dom-performancecontainertiming-intersectionrect①\">intersectionRect</a></code> set to the bounding rectangle of <var>record</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#container-timing-record-paintedregion\" id=\"ref-for-container-timing-record-paintedregion②\">paintedRegion</a></p>\n       </li><li data-md=\"\">\n        <p><code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#dom-performancecontainertiming-size\" id=\"ref-for-dom-performancecontainertiming-size②\">size</a></code> set to the total area of <var>record</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#container-timing-record-paintedregion\" id=\"ref-for-container-timing-record-paintedregion③\">paintedRegion</a></p>\n       </li><li data-md=\"\">\n        <p><code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#dom-performancecontainertiming-lastpaintedelement\" id=\"ref-for-dom-performancecontainertiming-lastpaintedelement①\">lastPaintedElement</a></code> set to <var>record</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#container-timing-record-lastnewpaintedareaelement\" id=\"ref-for-container-timing-record-lastnewpaintedareaelement①\">lastNewPaintedAreaElement</a></p>\n       </li><li data-md=\"\">\n        <p><code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://wicg.github.io/container-timing/#dom-performancecontainertiming-rootelement\" id=\"ref-for-dom-performancecontainertiming-rootelement①\">rootElement</a></code> set to <var>containerRoot</var></p>\n      </li></ul>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/performance-timeline/#dfn-queue-a-performanceentry\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-queue-a-performanceentry\">Queue the PerformanceEntry</a> <var>entry</var>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}